data.description: Wanting a new build with all the extras?? Look no further! This home comes with the fridge, washer and dryer, water softener, blinds, and a playset in the backyard. Escape the hustle and bustle as you step into this hidden gem, nestled away from the busy streets of San Antonio. This enchanting home welcomes you with an elegant staircase, setting the tone for the unique features that await inside.  As you enter, the upgraded ceramic tile flooring leads you into an inviting eat-in kitchen adorned with beautiful quartz countertops. The kitchen is bathed in natural light streaming through five stunning windows, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The primary bathroom offers a luxurious retreat, providing a resort-like feel for unwinding after a long day. Immerse yourself in tranquility and pamper yourself in this spa-like space. Additionally, an inviting game room awaits, providing the perfect setting for entertainment, relaxation, or family gatherings. Located in the highly sought-after far West Side, this home offers the perfect blend of tranquility and convenience. Just one mile away, you'll find an H-E-B for your grocery needs, as well as nearby coffee shops, restaurants, salons, and fast-food options. Welcome to your new home!
